Class SingleThreadPacketProcessor

  • PacketProcessorComponent
    • MappedPacketProcessor
      • FixedThreadPoolPacketProcessor
        • com.github.yona168.giraffe.net.messenger.packetprocessor.SingleThreadPacketProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PacketProcessor

    public class SingleThreadPacketProcessor
extends FixedThreadPoolPacketProcessor

    A interface PacketProcessor that processes all packets on one thread. This is convinient if packets must be processed in a sequential order. Creating an instance of this class is equivalent to creating a class FixedThreadPoolPacketProcessor with a thread amount of 1

    See Also:
    interface PacketProcessor, class FixedThreadPoolPacketProcessor
